  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施部署流程图，核心是用户通过负载均衡器发起请求，然后经过一系列判断节点来决定最终走向。我先描述一下整体结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1",
        "D1",
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解用户侧是Infra_LoadBalancer。那A1这个节点是做什么用的？是工作节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，A1是Infra_WorkerNode，负责接收从负载均衡器过来的流量。另外我注意到还有一个H1也是负载均衡器，这个其实是辅助上下文用的，和U类似。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "H1",
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，那我先把U指向A1，同时H1也指向A1。然后A1后面应该接什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "A1后面接一个工具节点T1，是Infra_IngressController，然后T1再指回A1形成循环。之后A1还要引出第一个判断节点D1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "T1",
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "T1指回A1？这是表示IngressController处理完再回到工作节点吗？还有D1的判断条件是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "A1",
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，T1处理完返回A1。D1也是Infra_IngressController，但这里是作为决策点，判断是否需要走C1路径。如果Yes，走C1再到U；如果No，走A2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "U",
        "A2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，D1的两条分支我加上了。A2是另一个负载均衡器Infra_LoadBalancer对吧？它后面接D2？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "A2",
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，A2是Infra_LoadBalancer。D2是Infra_EtcdCluster，作为第二个判断节点。D2为Yes时走R1，为No时走AT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A2",
        "D2",
        "R1",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "R1是Infra_IngressController吗？它后面指向APPD？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R1",
        "APPD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，R1是IngressController，APPD是Infra_EtcdCluster。然后APPD要指向AT，AT也是Infra_EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "AT后面有两个分支对吧？一个是Needs App Execution，一个是No Execution Needed？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。Needs App Execution走APP_ACK，是Infra_LoadBalancer，然后到U2。No Execution Needed直接到U2。U2是Infra_EtcdCluster，也是用户侧的终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "结构我画完了。现在来定义样式类别吧？用户节点用蓝色，助手节点用绿色，决策点用黄色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "classDef user",
        "classDef assistant",
        "classDef decision"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，user类用#E3F2FD填充，#90CAF9描边。assistant类用#E8F5E9填充，#A5D6A7描边。decision用#FFF8E1填充，#FFD54F描边。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "assistant",
        "decision"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式定义好了。应用类别：U和U2是user，A1、A2、C1、R1还有AT是assistant，D1和D2是decision。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "U2",
        "A1",
        "A2",
        "C1",
        "R1",
        "AT",
        "D1",
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有app类别，APPD和APP_ACK，用紫色#F3E5F5填充，#CE93D8描边。T1和H1是tool类别，用#FBE9E7填充，#FFAB91描边。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD",
        "APP_ACK",
        "T1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了。不过我看到你之前提到R2和CALL，但在流程里没有用到，需要加上吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R2",
        "CALL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，R2和CALL是多余的，从类别定义里删掉。另外assistant类别里也不应该有它们。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R2",
        "CALL"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已删除R2和CALL。我检查一下：assistant类别现在是A1、A2、C1、R1、AT，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "A2",
        "C1",
        "R1",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。再确认一下AT的标注，Needs App Execution和No Execution Needed这两条边要清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "AT到APP_ACK的边标注是Needs App Execution，AT到U2的直接边标注是No Execution Needed，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。还有D1的Yes和No、D2的Yes和No也要标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有判断分支的标注都加上了。最后检查一下：U是Infra_LoadBalancer，但代码里写的是Infra_LoadBalancer，我需要确认拼写。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "应该是Infra_LoadBalancer，不是adbalancer。你看到的可能是笔误，统一用正确的拼写。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正。另外我注意到additi可能是additional的缩写，但在图里没有单独节点，只是APPD代表Additional Data Check对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 27,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，APPD就是Additional Data的缩写，代表附加数据检查后的应用节点。finalizati对应的是最后的U2终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 28,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有节点和样式都配置完成了。我最终确认一下类别：user有U、U2；assistant有A1、A2、C1、R1、AT；decision有D1、D2；app有APPD、APP_ACK；tool有T1、H1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "assistant",
        "decision",
        "app",
        "tool"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 29,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，就是这个结构。从用户负载均衡器进入，经过工作节点、IngressController判断、Etcd集群决策，最后根据是否需要应用执行走到终点。",
